is how well traveled she is.

58:06.657 --> 58:08.136
Well, what else
would she talk about?

58:08.659 --> 58:09.703
Thank you, dear.

58:12.140 --> 58:14.926
The air in Ibiza,

58:16.884 --> 58:18.495
there's really nothing like it.

58:19.931 --> 58:21.889
I'm getting misty,
just thinking about it.

58:21.933 --> 58:23.804
Peter, put our agent in touch
with them, all right?

58:23.848 --> 58:26.764
