get it screened.

59:05.890 --> 59:06.934
-Maybe.
-Yeah. Yeah.

59:07.152 --> 59:08.849
- Morocco.
-Yeah.

59:09.197 --> 59:12.157
Uh, Richard, uh,
no, no, no,

59:12.200 --> 59:13.898
that'll only encourage her.

59:13.941 --> 59:15.900
...we've noticed
that it's allowed us

59:15.943 --> 59:19.120
